invalid.svelte:2:10 lint/a11y/noRedundantRoles  FIXABLE  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

  × Using the role attribute 'article' on the 'article' element is redundant, because it is implied by its semantics.
  
    1 │ <!-- should generate diagnostics -->
